'Spin chain' calls.

Spin chain the gears (plus), spin chain and circulate the gears (c4).

sdr> /program = C4
C4
sdr> sides pass the ocean ; extend
| 2B^  3Gv  4G^  3Bv
| 
| 1B^  2Gv  1G^  4Bv
sdr> spin chain the gears
| 1B^  2Gv  3G^  2Bv
| 
| 4B^  1Gv  4G^  3Bv
sdr> spin chain and circulate the gears
| 3B^  2Gv  3G^  4Bv
| 
| 2B^  1Gv  4G^  1Bv
sdr> trade the wave
| 3Gv  4B^  3Bv  2G^
| 
| 4Gv  1B^  2Bv  1G^
sdr> spin chain the gears but turn the star 1/2
| 3Bv  1G^  4Gv  4B^
| 
| 2Bv  2G^  3Gv  1B^
sdr> spin chain and circulate the gears but turn the star 1/2
| 2Gv  1B^  2Bv  3G^
| 
| 1Gv  4B^  3Bv  4G^
sdr> deuces wild
| 1Gv  2B^  1Bv  4G^
| 
| 2Gv  3B^  4Bv  3G^
sdr> left allemande
| 1G^  1B^
| 
| 2Bv  4Gv
| 
| 2G^  4B^
| 
| 3Bv  3Gv
sdr> promenade home
|      3Gv  3Bv
| 
| 4B>            2G<
| 
| 4G>            2B<
| 
|      1B^  1G^
sdr> /exit
